{
  "text": "The there seems to have been created by this logos, to me anyway, a large percentage of entities whose distortion was toward warfare, and that we had the Maldek and the Mars experience. And now Earth, it seems that Venus was the exception to what we could almost call the rule of warfare. Was this correct and was this envisioned and planned into the construction of the archetypical mind? Possibly not with respect particularly to warfare as we have experienced it, but to the extreme action to polarization and consciousness. This form of expression of hostility is an interesting result which is apparently concomitant with the tool making ability, the choice of the logos to use the life form with the grasping thumb is the decision to which this type of a warfare may be traced.",
